      "sources": "Guide Inclusion & Diversité ISC Paris 2023-2024 (8p)\nhttps://www.iscparis.com/isc-paris-responsabilite-societale-diversite-et-inclusion/\nhttps://www.iscparis.com/isc-paris-labels-et-accreditations/\nhttps://www.iscparis.com/diversite-et-inclusion/\nhttps://www.iscparis.com/les-entreprises-etudiantes-de-lisc-paris/\nhttps://www.iscparis.com/program/dimension-inclusive-de-la-rse/\nhttps://www.iscparis.com/program/le-bachelor-specialisation-management-durable-rse/"
